summary: AN ORDINANCE releasing two easements for storm drain purposes over certain real property in Section 22, Township 25 North, Range 4 East, W.M., (being portions of Tracts 121, 122, 141, 142, and 143 of the unrecorded plat of Broadmoor), and accepting easements in lieu thereof.
